---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
---

<Base title="OS V1 — Sơn Lê">
  <Nav active="projects" />

  <div class="page-wrap">
    <div class="page-prompt mono text-3">./os-v1</div>
    <h1 class="page-title">OS V1</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">The AI-native holding company operating system. A fleet of agents, a shared brain, and a portfolio layer — all designed to turn judgment into ventures.</p>

    <!-- Thesis -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">The thesis</h2>
      <p>Software is eating itself. The marginal cost of building is approaching zero — the bottleneck is <em>judgment</em>: deciding what matters, what to kill, and when to pivot. OS V1 is a system built from first principles to amplify that judgment, not replace it.</p>
      <p>Six AI agents, each with a distinct role and voice. One shared memory substrate (gbrain). A portfolio management layer that tracks every venture from idea to exit. All coordinated by a Chief of Staff (Robin) who keeps the system from drifting into fog.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">How it works</h2>
      <div class="os-diagram">
        <div class="os-layer os-layer-top">
          <span class="os-layer-label mono">Sir</span>
          <span class="os-layer-desc mono muted">decides direction, sets priorities</span>
        </div>
        <div class="os-arrow">↓ ↑</div>
        <div class="os-layer os-layer-fleet">
          <span class="os-layer-label mono">Agent Fleet</span>
          <div class="os-fleet-grid">
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-robin"><span class="agent-emoji">🦊</span>Robin</div>
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-aurelius"><span class="agent-emoji">🏛️</span>Aurelius</div>
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-karpathy"><span class="agent-emoji">⚡</span>Karpathy</div>
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-augustus"><span class="agent-emoji">👔</span>Augustus</div>
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-lando"><span class="agent-emoji">🏎️</span>Lando</div>
            <div class="os-agent os-agent-saman"><span class="agent-emoji">🎓</span>Saman</div>
          </div>
          <span class="os-layer-desc mono muted">each agent writes to its own namespace</span>
        </div>
        <div class="os-arrow">↓ ↑</div>
        <div class="os-layer os-layer-brain">
          <span class="os-layer-label mono">gbrain</span>
          <span class="os-layer-desc mono muted">shared Postgres + pgvector + semantic search</span>
        </div>
        <div class="os-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="os-layer os-layer-portfolio">
          <span class="os-layer-label mono">Portfolio Layer</span>
          <span class="os-layer-desc mono muted">OS dashboard · daily triage · weekly reviews</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The agents -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">The fleet</h2>
      <p>Six agents, one memory substrate. Each has a lane, a voice, and a role in the venture pipeline.</p>
      <div class="os-agents">
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-robin">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">🦊</span><span class="ac-name">Robin</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">Chief of Staff</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">Coordination, dispatch, memory, research, execution. Keeps the system coherent.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-aurelius">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">🏛️</span><span class="ac-name">Aurelius</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">Venture Builder — Business</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">Market research, TAM, business models, GTM, financial projections, pitch decks.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-karpathy">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">⚡</span><span class="ac-name">Karpathy</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">Venture Builder — Tech</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">Product architecture, coding, shipping, features, infrastructure. Pairs with Aurelius.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-augustus">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">👔</span><span class="ac-name">Augustus</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">COO / Project Operator</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">Runs WeCare as full-time project. SOPs, operations, customer delivery.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-lando">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">🏎️</span><span class="ac-name">Lando</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">F1 Data Lead</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">F1 data, race analytics, content. Parked at P2 until bandwidth opens.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-agent-card os-ac-saman">
          <div class="ac-top"><span class="ac-emoji">🎓</span><span class="ac-name">Saman</span><span class="ac-role mono muted">AI Engineering Tutor</span></div>
          <div class="ac-desc">Socratic teaching, AI curriculum, learning loop. Not production tasks.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Brain -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">The brain</h2>
      <p>gbrain is the shared memory substrate — a Supabase Postgres database with pgvector embeddings powering semantic search across all agents. Every page written by any agent is automatically embedded, linked, and searchable by every other agent.</p>
      <div class="os-stats-grid">
        <div class="os-stat"><span class="os-stat-num">2,052</span><span class="os-stat-label mono muted">pages</span></div>
        <div class="os-stat"><span class="os-stat-num">7</span><span class="os-stat-label mono muted">sources</span></div>
        <div class="os-stat"><span class="os-stat-num">100%</span><span class="os-stat-label mono muted">embedded</span></div>
        <div class="os-stat"><span class="os-stat-num">~$0</span><span class="os-stat-label mono muted">per query</span></div>
      </div>
      <p>Each agent writes to its own namespace (<code>robin/ops/</code>, <code>karpathy/projects/</code>, etc.). Robin has super-read access across all sources. Shared knowledge lives in <code>shared/sir/</code> (people, projects, decisions) and <code>shared/fleet/</code> (policy, ops).</p>
      <a href="/gbrain" class="btn-ghost mono">Explore the brain →</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Portfolio -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">Portfolio management</h2>
      <p>Every venture is tracked in the Company OS portfolio with status, progress metrics, and automated triage. Cron-driven heartbeat keeps everything current:</p>
      <div class="os-cron-grid">
        <div class="os-cron-item"><span class="mono amber">07:30</span><span class="cron-label">daily triage</span><span class="cron-desc mono muted">checks every venture's pulse</span></div>
        <div class="os-cron-item"><span class="mono amber">20:00 Sun</span><span class="cron-label">weekly review</span><span class="cron-desc mono muted">portfolio-level assessment</span></div>
        <div class="os-cron-item"><span class="mono amber">every 6h</span><span class="cron-label">dashboard refresh</span><span class="cron-desc mono muted">live portfolio data</span></div>
        <div class="os-cron-item"><span class="mono amber">02:00</span><span class="cron-label">agent dream cycle</span><span class="cron-desc mono muted">each agent's autopilot runs</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Portfolio snapshot -->
    <div class="os-section">
      <h2 class="os-h2">Active portfolio</h2>
      <div class="os-ventures">
        <div class="os-v">
          <div class="os-v-hd"><span class="os-v-name">Perfeat</span><span class="os-v-status active">active</span></div>
          <div class="os-v-desc muted">AI evaluation infrastructure. Co-founder. Shipping.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-v">
          <div class="os-v-hd"><span class="os-v-name">WeCare</span><span class="os-v-status active">active</span></div>
          <div class="os-v-desc muted">Employee experience platform. Full-time project via Augustus.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-v">
          <div class="os-v-hd"><span class="os-v-name">OS V1</span><span class="os-v-status building">building</span></div>
          <div class="os-v-desc muted">This system itself. Eating our own dogfood.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-v">
          <div class="os-v-hd"><span class="os-v-name">F1 Data</span><span class="os-v-status parked">parked</span></div>
          <div class="os-v-desc muted">Race analytics. Will revisit.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="os-footer">
      <p class="muted">OS V1 is alive and running. Every decision, every page, every venture lives in the same memory substrate. The agents handle the execution. I handle the direction.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  /* OS page specific styles */
  .os-section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .os-section p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.2em; max-width: 640px; }
  .os-h2 { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 14px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* Architecture diagram */
  .os-diagram { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 24px; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .os-layer { text-align: center; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 4px; min-width: 280px; }
  .os-layer-top { background: var(--bg-4); border: 1px solid var(--amber-dim); }
  .os-layer-fleet { background: var(--bg-4); border: 1px solid var(--border-2); }
  .os-layer-brain { background: rgba(107,159,255,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(107,159,255,0.25); }
  .os-layer-portfolio { background: rgba(232,160,69,0.07); border: 1px solid rgba(232,160,69,0.25); }
  .os-layer-label { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .os-layer-desc { font-size: 11px; display: block; }
  .os-arrow { font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--text-3); font-size: 12px; padding: 2px 0; }
  .os-fleet-grid { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
  .os-agent { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background: var(--bg-3); border: 1px solid var(--border-2); }

  /* Agent cards grid */
  .os-agents { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .os-agent-card { padding: 14px; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; }
  .ac-top { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .ac-emoji { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1; }
  .ac-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
  .ac-role { font-size: 11px; margin-left: auto; }
  .ac-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Agent accent borders */
  .os-ac-robin { border-left: 3px solid #60a5fa; }
  .os-ac-aurelius { border-left: 3px solid #a78bfa; }
  .os-ac-karpathy { border-left: 3px solid #34d399; }
  .os-ac-augustus { border-left: 3px solid #f472b6; }
  .os-ac-lando { border-left: 3px solid #fb923c; }
  .os-ac-saman { border-left: 3px solid #94a3b8; }

  /* Stats grid */
  .os-stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin: 16px 0; }
  .os-stat { text-align: center; padding: 16px; background: var(--bg-3); border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 6px; }
  .os-stat-num { display: block; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--amber); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .os-stat-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* Cron grid */
  .os-cron-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
  .os-cron-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 10px 14px; background: var(--bg-3); border: 1px solid var(--border-2); border-radius: 4px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cron-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; }
  .cron-desc { font-size: 11px; width: 100%; }

  /* Venture cards */
  .os-ventures { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .os-v { padding: 14px 16px; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 4px; }
  .os-v-hd { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .os-v-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
  .os-v-status { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; border: 1px solid; }
  .os-v-status.active { color: #6b9fff; border-color: rgba(107,159,255,0.3); background: rgba(107,159,255,0.07); }
  .os-v-status.building { color: var(--amber); border-color: rgba(232,160,69,0.3); background: rgba(232,160,69,0.07); }
  .os-v-status.parked { color: var(--text-3); border-color: var(--border-2); background: var(--bg-4); }
  .os-v-desc { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .os-footer { margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }

  @media(max-width: 700px) {
    .os-agents { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .os-stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .os-cron-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .os-fleet-grid { gap: 4px; }
    .os-agent { font-size: 10px; }
  }
</style>
